OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1776791155
OL,3,CParents head to Australia for murder
OL,4,Ctrial into motel car park stabbing of
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FThe parents of a County Durham man are
OL,8,Ftravelling to Australia ahead of a
OL,9,Fmurder trial into the stabbing of
OL,10,Ftheir son in a motel car park.
OL,12,FRoyce Mallett was living and working
OL,13,Fin New South Wales to earn money to
OL,14,Fsupport his partner and two young
OL,15,Fchildren when he was fatally wounded
OL,16,Fin July 2024.
OL,18,FThe 30-year-old, whose parents live in
OL,19,FHaswell, travelled to Australia to lay
OL,20,Fasphalt in March 2024 after being
OL,21,Funable to find work in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
