PN,42502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1776791155
OL,3,CParents head to Australia for murder
OL,4,Ctrial into motel car park stabbing of
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FHe was due to return home that summer
OL,8,Ffor his son's second birthday but at
OL,9,Faround 6pm on 8 July 2024, Mr Mallett
OL,10,Fwas stabbed while in a car in a motel
OL,11,Fcar park in Albury.
OL,13,FMore than 18 months on and his mother
OL,14,FFelicity Mallett is packed and ready
OL,15,Ffor the long journey to see the man
OL,16,Faccused of killing her son stand trial.
OL,18,FOn Monday (20 April) she told ITV News
OL,19,FTyne Tees attending the trial for her
OL,20,Fson was something she has to do.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1776791155
OL,3,CParents head to Australia for murder
OL,4,Ctrial into motel car park stabbing of
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,F"We know it's going to be very, very
OL,8,Fhard because we're going to see bits
OL,9,Fthat we don't particularly want to
OL,10,Fsee," she said.
OL,12,F"We're going to see the the knife. His
OL,13,Fclothes, bits and pieces that were
OL,14,Fleft in the car. It just has to be
OL,15,Fdone. It's got to be sorted out."
OL,17,FMr Mallett's family have already had
OL,18,Fto endure raising #20,000 to get his
OL,19,Fbody brought back home in 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
