PN,42504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1776791155
OL,3,CParents head to Australia for murder
OL,4,Ctrial into motel car park stabbing of
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FThey were able to give him a funeral
OL,8,Fat home in County Durham but Mrs
OL,9,FMallett said that had not taken away
OL,10,Fany of the family's pain.
OL,12,F"You can't have a normal day," added
OL,13,FMrs Mallett. "I walk through the
OL,14,Fvillage - I walk through the town, at
OL,15,FPeterlee, and people know me. They
OL,16,Fknow me already. I'll get a tap on the
OL,17,Fshoulder like that, as if to say,
OL,18,F'you're the lady who lost her son the
OL,19,Fother year...in Australia'.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
