FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1776791155
OL,3,CParents head to Australia for murder
OL,4,Ctrial into motel car park stabbing of
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,F"It's there all the time. Maybe we can
OL,8,Fget some justice for him done (and)
OL,9,Ftry and get back to normal if we can.
OL,10,FHopefully."
OL,12,FFollowing the attack in July 2024, a
OL,13,Fman was arrested and reportedly
OL,14,Fcharged with murder by local police.
OL,16,FThe trial is due to start in Australia
OL,17,Fon Monday 27 April.
OL,26,@pD@_pmpD@cpn
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
