PN,42506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1776791155
OL,3,CParents head to Australia for murder
OL,4,Ctrial into motel car park stabbing of
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FThe family has been told it is likely
OL,8,Fto last around three weeks and Mrs
OL,9,FMallett and her husband are determined
OL,10,Fto be in court every single day.
OL,12,FDavid Summers-Smith, 30, is on trial.
OL,13,FThe family has been told he has
OL,14,Fpleaded not guilty to a charge of
OL,15,Fmurder and the case was committed to
OL,16,Fthe Supreme Court of New South Wales.
OL,18,FIt is thought then it could be around
OL,19,Ffive weeks before a result is
OL,20,Fdelivered in the trial.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
